{"tid":739461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為女學生按摩撫摸胸部私處   美31歲華裔男被判緩刑堅持沒有做錯","createTime":"2018-07-12T06:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T11:18:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d939140110837d8488cb28701befff0c8d963f91","tid":739461,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180712/_2018071213172727078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180712%2F_2018071213172727078.jpg&h=c2cb6812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國芝加哥一名31歲華裔按摩男技師為19歲女按摩時，疑「不當撫摸」對方胸部、臀部及私處，被裁定性虐待及性侵犯罪成立，最終判緩刑兩年及罰款2500美元。法官指，被告沒有犯罪記錄，遂判以緩刑。被告在判刑時讀出信件，堅持自己沒有做錯，但尊重法庭判決。<br />\n<br />\n案發生在2017年10月，19歲女學生到伊文斯頓市按摩店「Art of Health spa」按摩。她表示，31歲華裔男子王凱（音譯）為她按摩時，將手伸到毛巾下，觸摸她的胸部、臀部及私處，儘管她曾試圖反抗和離開，但王凱將手臂環抱她，甚至將她抱起來。她於是報警，將王拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n今年5月，王凱被裁定「刑事性虐罪」和「刑事性侵未遂罪」兩項罪成，但更為嚴重的「性侵罪」則未成立。至上周四（5日），法官判處王凱緩刑兩年，罰款2500美元，並將他列入性犯罪者名單中。他需提供DNA樣本，以納入執法人員大數據資料庫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1263912/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1263912%2F&d=b%2BL7yZQHkTtw9lNrjqR4f7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=71f7f827\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1263912%2F&h=193c2ea4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1263912/</a>"},{"pid":"04d186f075cd732c4f04c74ca88bd8f568e04f54","tid":739461,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:30:11.000Z","msg":"王凱 (Kai Wang) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b172a42a047ebc71d1decfa5c21228c40ece622","tid":739461,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:30:50.000Z","msg":"摸波=性虐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\